  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">You inflict a curse where an enemy's life force spills out to creatures who attack it in close proximity. On a failed save, the target is cursed. Creatures who damage the target with lethal melee attacks regain 2 hit points. If the target is also bleeding, the healing increases by your spellcasting modifier.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The range for this spell varies depending on the number of actions used to cast this spell; touch for 1 action, 30 feet for 2 actions.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Success </strong>The creature is afflicted by the curse for 1 round.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Failure </strong>The creature is afflicted by the curse for 1 minute.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but the creature also takes 1d4 persistent bleed damage.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Heightened(+1)</strong> The healing from the curse increases by 2 and the persistent bleed damage increases by 1.</p>"
    },
